wow. I'm gonna update because kayla is in the shower, and she doesnt have any cable and no one is online.

just moved out of my house today, gonna stay at kayla's till i move to tally.

i am excited to see her tho and stay here.

hopefully gonna have a good night tonight.

maybe some partying? i hope. hah.

i saw lauranne today too she is the cutest thing ever. 

okay i dont think anyone cares about this post anymore, i'm just really bored.

I'm gonna jump on my bed so my gerbil comes out of her hiding. 

gr.

It's 9 in the morning. How much does that suck?
Reallly bad.
I love getting paid for doing nothing.

Yesterday I hung out with Tom woo!

...and it was so hard seeing you. 
blah.

Today is mother's day, and I don't have a mother.
Just a memory.
The closest thing to a mother I have is Kayla's mom, my aunt jo, and Nana.
I love them all very much, but they aren't my own. They have kids of their own.They are always there when I need them, and I thank them for that. I hope they know, because they are all wonderful people. But I miss my mom. There's no other realtionship quite like a mother and her child, and I only got to experience that for 13 years, I guess i'm lucky cause some people never get to. I love you mom and I forgive you for all the things you've done. Happy Mother's Day, i will visit you today. Kayla I want you to come with me. 

Anyway, work is soon, thank god i don't have to work ALL day just 10-3, bummer.

wow i haven't updated this thing in forever. 
Nothing new. 

I offically love the people i work with. <3

So I'm happy about life...
except for ONE THING.
and..i hate it. 
that always happens but whatever.
i'll get over it in time.

my gerbil is annoying at night.
sometime i just want to kill it.

wow i'm moving soon, and that just awesome.

maybe i should start updating this thing again
i feel so out of touch lol
I'm not sure tho...


hmmm..

hey.






guess what.





I finally got a car.





!





=D

So, I don't write in my lj too much anymore, but i'm having so many thoughts run through my head, especially since my bad day yesterday. I'm not even exactly sure why it was bad, I didn't do anything and nothing happened, but I thought about a lot of stuff. I'm not sad nor happy, but for some reason life seems kind of worthless right now. It's sad when you're desperatly looking forward to going away for a few days to a different state just to get away from your life. I dont even get why this is all coming into my mind now because really nothing bad is going on, i dont know. Christmas isn't so jolly right now, and believe me I wish it was because I look forward to Christmas as being a time to be with your friends and family and really feeling like you're a part of something special. I dont feel like I am anything special. I'm just kind of stuck in this boring rutt that's called my life. I'm looking forward to a few things in 2005 like being able to drive, and graduating high school and moving away from home. I'm just so bored with life right now, and I can't wait for something interesting to happen. I wish time could skip to July so I can be 18 and not in Stuart anymore. I'm hoping that my last 7 months here will be fun and I can feel like a belong, and I have happy memories to leave to, and maybe even for people to be sad when I leave. Things change, people change, life changes, and I do love change, but I wish some things would stay the same. It's too much to ask for people to stay the same, friendships change either for the worse or for the better. I feel so close to some of my friends right now, and some I feel like i'm pretending to have this great friendship with, when I know it's really not like that anymore, cause ya know...people change. It just happens that way. I'm not sure why. To keep us on our toes I guess. I wish I didn't have to pretend anymore, and that we're really that great, but I'm not too sure that that's true, that if I stop pretending things will just drift away. Maybe I'll be proven wrong. hopefully. 

so yeah me rambling isn't fun. ok bye.

omg kayla you are the best.

<3333333333333333333333333

I don't really understand why it's so hard for people to be honest. 

i don't get it...

I dont know what to think.


blah.

I was tired all day.

and...

I was supposed to go to Brandon's house today, but brook had to paint her room and stuff, so we couldn't go. I had fun painting and all, but i really wanted to see him. =/

maybe this weekend?

hopefully.

haha i'm such an idiot... anyway the highlight of my day yesterday was when some 5 year old kid came up to me in the park and said "penis! I have a penis!" and walked away. this is in my house: how cool is that? It dances too.

then cruisers

then my house.

hm.

<3

I'm thankful for a lot but i'm not writing a paragraph.

I almost got in trouble. whew.

<3

Yay thanksgiving is on thursday i'm so excited to get fat <3

hehe <3

I haven't updated too much. 

Things in life are actually not too bad. 

Some people act immature about certain things, but i'm over it. Really.

We also met two guys while we were down there. We hung out and then saw a movie with them. They were really cool. The movie really really sucked tho, it wouldn't end!! Hopefully we're hanging out later. 

I have driving school today, i'm on my way to getting my license. finally damn. School on saturday sucks, but at least it's leading up to a good thing. I don't have to work today yay!

blah.

I know my life isn't that bad, but it's okay to get upset from time to time.

I feel so alone and no matter how much people tell me that i'm not, and that they care, i still don't feel that. I still feel alone. 



...



er.

So mad shit has been brewing up lately. 

It's gotten out of hand.

Me and maria are good now, because she handled it really maturely and i respect her for that. I was honest with her, and i'm glad I was. It is so much better than lying. 

I'm glad things are semi-okay, but i doubt the other part of the problem will ever be okay.

SAT's sucked and my brain hurt. I didn't have to work today though. That was a big plus +++. I have nothing to do tonight. blah.

So...

Denny's in a strange town after the concert was great, good times...good times. *straw sticks in hair and massive amounts of laughter* 

Oh man <3333333

Hopefully tonight i'm going to the mall to meet up with emily =) and then hang out with kayla when she gets off work. 








...i don't even know why i even try anymore. goodbye sounds good.

Kayla picked me up we went to the mall, goodwill, wal-mart and the halloween store to go shopping for our halloween costumes. We saw Lauranne and Caroline and we tried on tons of hats and stuff <3. 

Then me and kayla went to noel's and made a chicken sandwich, yummy. lol. 

Came home, made our costumes, which i think are very cute. Pirates rock. 





ah..i'm confused.

I love how when i'm content and happy with life, my dad has to make me feel like shit. I rarely watch tv but the one time I do go out there to watch tv he yells at me for being lazy and not doing anything ever, He says I come home everyday and do nothing. and sometimes thats true. I'm sorry i'm not good at sports, and that I decided to follow through with my travel and tourism academy and that I come home from school at 1:30. I'm sorry i'm not a straight A student. I'm only a B. I'm not perfect in any aspect, and I never will be. I'm sorry that i disappointed him, and that i'm not in any after school activities. and it sucks that he's right about me. I'm a sucky high school student with nothing to do. I am lazy sometimes, but I never mean to be. I want to be involved, I want to be smarter, but it looks like it's too late now. that makes me sad, I wasted all this time. Now i'm worried about getting into college, and that i'll have to go to IRCC or something. I just want to get out of this town and start a new life, even though it scares me to death...




you can save me...
